'''Level 904''' is the 905<sup>th</sup> level of [[The Backrooms]].
==<span style="font-family:Work Sans">Description</span>==
{{Blurquote|image=Watching.png|person=<span style="font-family:Rubik Glitch">???</span>|quote-text=..I can't sleep.. They watch me every day and night..}}
{{Blurimage|file=Watching.png|caption=A picture of '''Level 904'''.|hovertext=They won't stop..}}
'''Level 904 is always watching you.''' 

'''Level 904''' wasn't always the peaceful haven with tons of auroras. Early records indicate that the level existed in a highly unstable Deadzone state, with a hostile sky and extreme psychological danger. This version is now thought to be an earlier version of the level that preceded an unidentified large-scale environmental stabilization event.

'''Level 904''' was created using a undisclosed software/hardware developed by [[M.E.G.|M.E.G]]. It is said to be a program ran on a supercomputer for potential to create, store and manage Levels in the Backrooms. The program is said to be made using an unknown programming laungage. It can also '''<code>''<big>[<><><><><><><><><><>]</big>''</code>'''. 

All rights involving '''Level 904''' are owned by [[M.E.G.|M.E.G]]. <br />

It is also rumored that '''Level 904''' is '''<code>''<big>[<><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><>]</big>''</code>'''.
==<span style="font-family:Work Sans">Entities</span>==
The eyes that watch you in the sky disgusing as an aurora are the only entity.
==<span style="font-family:Work Sans">Colonies & Outposts</span>==
All colonies and outposts are eradicated. The only remains of the 8 colonies are destroyed bunkers and wooden houses.
==<span style="font-family:Work Sans">Entrances & Exits</span>==
